    "p": "A slim face with gray eyes and a humorous smile appeared in the doorway.",
    "len": 14
  },
  "323": {
    "p": "&ldquo;Got a hammer?&rdquo;",
    "len": 5
  },
  "324": {
    "p": "&ldquo;No&mdash;sorry. Maybe Mrs. Twelve, or whatever she goes by, has one.&rdquo;",
    "len": 15
  },
  "325": {
    "p": "The stranger advanced into the room.",
    "len": 6
  },
  "326": {
    "p": "&ldquo;You an inmate of this asylum?&rdquo;",
    "len": 8
  },
  "327": {
    "p": "Amory nodded.",
    "len": 2
  },
  "328": {
    "p": "&ldquo;Awful barn for the rent we pay.&rdquo;",
    "len": 9
  },
  "329": {
    "p": "Amory had to agree that it was.",
    "len": 7
  },
  "330": {
    "p": "&ldquo;I thought of the campus,&rdquo; he said, &ldquo;but they say there's so few freshmen that they're lost. Have to sit around and study for something to do.&rdquo;",
    "len": 33
  },
  "331": {
    "p": "The gray-eyed man decided to introduce himself.",
    "len": 8
  },
