    "len": 27
  },
  "2036": {
    "p": "&ldquo;You drunk?&rdquo; queried Amory with intense wisdom.",
    "len": 9
  },
  "2037": {
    "p": "She nodded coyly.",
    "len": 3
  },
  "2038": {
    "p": "&ldquo;Go home with him,&rdquo; he advised gravely. &ldquo;He brought you.&rdquo;",
    "len": 14
  },
  "2039": {
    "p": "At this point the noisy man in the background broke away from his detainers and approached.",
    "len": 16
  },
  "2040": {
    "p": "&ldquo;Say!&rdquo; he said fiercely. &ldquo;I brought this girl out here and you're butting in!&rdquo;",
    "len": 19
  },
  "2041": {
    "p": "Amory regarded him coldly, while the girl clung to him closer.",
    "len": 11
  },
  "2042": {
    "p": "&ldquo;You let go that girl!&rdquo; cried the noisy man.",
    "len": 11
  },
  "2043": {
    "p": "Amory tried to make his eyes threatening.",
    "len": 7
  },
  "2044": {
    "p": "&ldquo;You go to hell!&rdquo; he directed finally, and turned his attention to the girl.",
    "len": 16
  },
  "2045": {
    "p": "&ldquo;Love first sight,&rdquo; he suggested.",
    "len": 7
  },
  "2046": {
    "p": "&ldquo;I love you,&rdquo; she breathed and nestled close to him. She did have beautiful eyes.",
    "len": 17
  },
  "2047": {
    "p": "Some one leaned over and spoke in Amory's ear.",
    "len": 10
  },
  "2048": {
    "p": "&ldquo;That's just Margaret Diamond. She's drunk and this fellow here brought her. Better let her go.&rdquo;",
    "len": 20
  },
  "2049": {
    "p": "&ldquo;Let him take care of her, then!&rdquo; shouted Amory furiously. &ldquo;I'm no W. Y. C. A. worker, am I?&mdash;am I?&rdquo;",
    "len": 27
  },
  "2050": {
    "p": "&ldquo;Let her go!&rdquo;",
    "len": 5
  },
  "2051": {
    "p": "&ldquo;It's her hanging on, damn it! Let her hang!&rdquo;",
    "len": 12
  },
  "2052": {
    "p": "The crowd around the table thickened. For an instant a brawl threatened, but a sleek waiter bent back Margaret Diamond's fingers until she released her hold on Amory, whereupon she slapped the waiter furiously in the face and flung her arms about her raging original escort.",
    "len": 47
  },
  "2053": {
